 OUCH! For a man, this is a painful way to depart. The Edo State police command has arrested a middle-aged woman, Eki Ekhator, for allegedly killing her husband by forcibly pulling his genitals. The incident was said to have happened at Ukhiri community in Ikpoba-Okha Local Government Area of the state. Sources said the couple had a quarrel after Mrs Ekhator accused her husband of having an affair. On that fateful day, the source said, the deceased slapped his wife across the face and the woman went for his balls and held onto his manhood in a violent manner. The man was said to have collapsed and later confirmed dead at the hospital. It was learnt that the Homicide department of the state police command is   investigating the incident. Sources at the police headquarters said the suspect  blamed the incident on “the devil.”